findings.title: Owner can change the tax, marketing and liquidity fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify tax, marketing, and liquidity fees.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude from the fee.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing wallet
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing wallet.

findings.title: Owner can change max wallet size amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum wallet size amount.

findings.title: Owner can blacklist addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to blacklist addresses.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.

findings.title: Out of gas exception in includeInReward() function
findings.description: The function includeInReward() uses a loop to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the excluded addresses list is too long.

findings.title: Out of gas exception in _getCurrentSupply function
findings.description: The function _getCurrentSupply uses a loop to evaluate total supply and could be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Out of gas exception in removeBotFromBlacklist() function
findings.description: The function removeBotFromBlacklist() uses a loop to remove blacklisted addresses and could be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long blacklist.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.
